  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p>Install electrical appliances (mainly water purifier).</p><p>Troubleshoot and identify solutions to on-site technical problems involving electrical and mechanical systems equipment.</p><p>Submit daily task reports and able to multitask</p><p>Conduct basic user-training to customers and payment collection.</p><p>Coordinate with NCSC job scheduling work.</p><p>Any ad-hoc tasks that may be assigned as and when required</p><p>Knowledgeable in servicing home appliances will be an added advantage.<br /></p><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><p>- Basic drilling and basic plumbing skill</p><p>- Work requires local travel.</p><p>- Good communication skills</p><p>- Customer Service Oriented</p><p>- Must possess Class 3 driving license and own vehicle</p>",
