    "description": "<p>About CUCKOO International &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>At CUCKOO International, we are focused at providing a one-stop healthy home solution through our CUCKOO Healthy Home platform. Our journey started in October 2014, with the introduction of CUCKOO, the well-known home appliance brand from South Korea, to the local market. Since then, CUCKOO International has grown to be a Healthy Home Creator with its CUCKOO Healthy Home platform aimed at improving the quality of living through Beyond Standards products and services. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The CUCKOO Healthy Home platform is supported by four pillars and brands. While the fourth pillar has yet to be launched, the existing three pillars continues to support the platform with its own unique products and services – Healthy Appliances pillar with CUCKOO (Water Purifiers, Outdoor Filter, Air Purifiers, Induction hobs and Kitchenware), Healthy Lifestyle pillar with WonderLab (skincare retailer featuring &nbsp;Haruharu, WELL NATURE and WonderDewi) and the Healthy Home Care pillar with WonderKlean (indoor disinfection services). Each pillar will continue to expand to offer a more comprehensive range of Healthy Home products and services. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>As at April 2020, CUCKOO International has accumulated over 820K customers and has opened over 500 branches including Brandstores, Brandkiosks and Wonderstores nationwide. The company also recorded RM920 million revenue in 2019, celebrating a solid 112% year-on-year growth.</p>",
